{% call components.section("Positioning") -%}

  <h3>Inline</h3>
  <p>Inline alerts appear at the top of a container or a component and push other content down. Inline alerts also have no fixed width, they conform to the width of whatever container they’re placed in and they persist until a user dismisses them or navigates away from the page.</p>

  <div class="centered margin-top--4 margin-bottom--4">
    <img src="{{ '/assets/alert/alert-positioning-1.svg' | url }}" alt="Inline alert in context on a page">
  </div>

  <h3>Toast</h3>
  <p>Toast alerts slide in from the top right edge of the screen under the navigation and overlay content. Toast alerts also have a fixed width of 600px and they persist until they time out after eight seconds or when a user dismisses them.</p>

  <div class="centered margin-top--4 margin-bottom--4">
    <img src="{{ '/assets/alert/alert-positioning-2.svg' | url }}" alt="Toast alert in context on a page">
  </div>

{%- endcall %}

